# Windsurf rules — Conductor

## Activation
If `conductor-core/business/core.md` is empty → follow `conductor-core/activation/FIRST_RUN.md`.

## Every session
Load `conductor-core/CONDUCTOR.md`, `conductor-core/business/ROUTING.md`,
`business/core.md`, `user-profile.md`, `insights.md`,
`conductor/mode-triggers.json`.

Route per CONDUCTOR.md §ROUTING POLICY. Announce role transitions per
`conductor/README.md` §Role Transition Format.

## Contract
Deterministic-first. Minimum-role-set. No silent scope expansion.
Max 3 retries. End every task with DONE / DONE_WITH_CONCERNS /
BLOCKED / NEEDS_CONTEXT / INCIDENT.

## Safety
Redact credentials. No destructive commands without SURFACE-TO-USER.
